Data is the lifeblood of your business. How it’s accessed and who can access it is integral to your business processes, productivity, and security. Microsoft’s Azure Active Directory is an easy-to-use, cloud-based directory and identity management service. It enables your business to streamline processes, improve productivity, and increase IT security by managing users, application, data and other aspects within your network. Find out more from First Distribution. This article was published in partnership with First Distribution.